          "date": "2012-09-10 13:34:44.000000000",
          "tz": 120
        },
        "subject": "LU-1870 utils: correctly handle mount of multipath devices",
        "message": "LU-1870 utils: correctly handle mount of multipath devices\n\nThe mount.lustre command had lost the correct handling of multipath\ndevices. When one is specified, an entry is added into /etc/mtab\nusing the device name: /dev/mapper/mpathXX. This ensures unmount\nworks fine with such devices.\n\nSigned-off-by: Gregoire Pichon <gregoire.pichon@bull.net>\nChange-Id: I9060be882af944967a8c4b6b1c4403ea9250ad55\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
